// Convention: if an operation touches more than one repository or emits events
// alongside writes, wrap it in a.uow.Do(ctx, func(ctx context.Context, repos UoWRepos) error { ... })
// to keep the state change atomic. Single-repo reads and writes can call the repo directly.

